name: Super PC Engine Fan Deluxe: Special CD-ROM Vol. 1
overview: Super PCE Fan Deluxe Special CD-Rom Vol. 1 is a Miscellaneous game, developed by NEC and published by Tokuma Shoten, which was released in Japan in 1997. Super PC Engine Fan Deluxe Special CD-ROM Vol.1 contains demos for Angelique Special 2, Yuna FX, Nirgends and Fire Woman
